Paratype ♂, &quot;Basses Alpes S FRANCE 22.viii.1913 Wlsm. 1913-390 95935&quot; 
<normalizedToken id="359C3493FC7C8DE4916728E8657E2382" originalValue="“Paratype”">&quot;Paratype&quot;</normalizedToken>
&quot;Megacraspedus pentheres Wlsm. PARATYPE&quot;, genitalia slide 33662 (BMNH). Non-type material. France. 1 ♂, Dep. Alpes-Maritimes, 
<normalizedToken id="097D47AB0C2B9B571EE9D6B4E7FC09D6" originalValue="Saint-Sauveur-sur-Tinée">Saint-Sauveur-sur-Tinee</normalizedToken>
